text: Frasers Property is a company that manages real estate in many countries. It is a multi-national company. It has assets in Singapore, Southeast Asia, Australia, Europe, and China. The company headquarters is in Singapore. The stocks of the company is traded in the Singapore Exchange. Frasers Property Industrial is a strategic business unit of Frasers Property. It develops and manages industrial properties in Australia, Germany, the Netherlands and Austria. As of 31 December 2019, it had approximately S$5.4 billion of assets under management. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:1963 establishments in Asia Category:Real estate developers Category:Companies of Singapore
